So to deliver our exploit to the victim we need 2 things:
1: is to inject our csrfkey cookie into the victims html header
2: send a csrf attack with the known csrf.
So to do the first pont do a search, and check the request in burp. we get 2 GET request one is /?search=asd and another one is /academyLabHeader
and we have a new cookie: LastSearchTerm=asd
Send the /?search request to repeater and modify the url like: /?search=test%0d%0aSet-Cookie:%20csrfKey=vdP8Ftf0Q4ILlPrDExDoiBVNKi3CLjvo and we got a http 200.

